ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: Introductory biostats course geared for clinical research. Would recommend if student is interested in clinical research.
Quick overview of statistics needed in clinical investigation. I have already recommended this course to people.

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: course is not very directly useful right now for my research because I am more involved with basic science research but enjoyed the class.
Gave me a better understanding if basic stats and how to interpret stats in clinical investigations.
